abstract: Honda Motor is investigating fatal accident on Jan 18 in Houston that is possibly linked to Takata airbag, which can rupture.
lead_paragraph: Honda Motor is investigating the fatal crash of a driver on Jan. 19 as a possible sixth death linked to Takata airbags that can rupture.
snippet: Honda Motor is investigating the fatal crash of a driver on Jan. 19 as a possible sixth death linked to Takata airbags that can rupture.

headline.main: Crash Death May Be Tied to a Takata Airbag
